<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>gnome-panel</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>gnome-panel</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=$GNOME_PREFIX --libexecdir=$GNOME_PREFIX/sbin \
--localstatedir=/var/lib --sysconfdir=/etc/gnome --disable-gtk-doc &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

